ed by the hakeem Dáwood. (TA.)       -A2-  Also, (M, TA,) thus, without the art., but written by Az and J with it, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~in~u","text_ar":"الصِّنُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the K, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One of the days called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAmu AlEajuwzi","text_ar":"اَيَّامُ العَجُوزِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, K;) said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the first of those days."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M. [See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ejz","text_ar":"عجز"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["S","M","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}